Name: market for gypsum, mineral | gypsum, mineral | EN15804GD, U
Category: B:Mining and quarrying/08:Other mining and quarrying/081:Quarrying of stone, sand and clay/0810:Quarrying of stone, sand and clay
Description: Gypsum deposites are usually found at shallow depths and are scattered over large areas. The deposits are mined out by opencast method and usually by manual mining except in few semi mechanised mines in Rajasthan.
